        "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"fr\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Votre kit est prêt à télécharger</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f5f5f5;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001f4d 0%, #003d7a 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .header h1 {\n            font-size: 28px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .header-icon {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .logo {\n            display: inline-block;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            color: #ff8c00;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .content {\n            padding: 40px 30px;\n        }\n        .greeting {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: #001f4d;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .text-block {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #555;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .order-info {\n            background-color: #f0f7ff;\n            border-left: 4px solid #ff8c00;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin: 25px 0;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        .order-info strong {\n            color: #001f4d;\n        }\n        .download-box {\n            background-color: #e8f4f8;\n            border: 2px solid #ff8c00;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin: 25px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .download-box h3 {\n            color: #001f4d;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .download-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ff8c00;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 35px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .download-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e67e00;\n        }\n        .instructions {\n            background-color: #fef9f0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin: 25px 0;\n            font-size: 13px;\n        }\n        .instructions h3 {\n            color: #001f4d;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .instruction-item {\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n        }\n        .instruction-number {\n            background-color: #ff8c00;\n            color: white;\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-right: 12px;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n        }\n        .instruction-text {\n            flex: 1;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .support {\n            background-color: #e8f4f8;\n            border: 1px solid #b3d9e8;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin: 25px 0;\n            font-size: 13px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .support strong {\n            color: #001f4d;\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .footer {\n            background-color: #f5f5f5;\n            padding: 25px 30px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #999;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n        }\n        .footer-links {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .footer-links a {\n            color: #001f4d;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n        }\n        .footer-links a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .company-info {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #777;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <table class=\"container\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden;\">\n        <!-- HEADER -->\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"header\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001f4d 0%, #003d7a 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center;\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">📦</div>\n                <h1 style=\"font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: white;\">Votre kit est prêt !</h1>\n                <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 16px;\">Téléchargez maintenant</p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- CONTENT -->\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding: 40px 30px;\">\n                <p class=\"greeting\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #001f4d; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Bonjour,</p>\n\n                <p class=\"text-block\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    Merci pour votre achat ! Votre kit [NOM_PRODUIT] est maintenant disponible en téléchargement.\n                </p>\n\n                <!-- ORDER INFO -->\n                <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 25px 0;\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <td style=\"background-color: #f0f7ff; border-left: 4px solid #ff8c00; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px;\">\n                            <strong style=\"color: #001f4d;\">Produit :</strong> [NOM_PRODUIT]<br>\n                            <strong style=\"color: #001f4d;\">Date d'achat :</strong> [DATE_ACHAT]<br>\n                            <strong style=\"color: #001f4d;\">Montant :</strong> [MONTANT_ACHAT]\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n\n                <!-- DOWNLOAD SECTION -->\n                <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color: #e8f4f8; border: 2px solid #ff8c00; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center;\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>\n                            <h3 style=\"color: #001f4d; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">Cliquez ci-dessous pour télécharger votre kit</h3>\n                            <a href=\"[LIEN_TELECHARGEMENT]\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #ff8c00; color: white; padding: 15px 35px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0;\">⬇️ Télécharger le kit</a>\n                            <p style=\"margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #666;\">Lien valide pendant 30 jours</p>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n\n                <!-- INSTRUCTIONS -->\n                <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color: #fef9f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 25px 0;\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>\n                            <h3 style=\"color: #001f4d; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">💡 Instructions d'utilisation</h3>\n\n                            <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td style=\"background-color: #ff8c00; color: white; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 12px;\">1</td>\n                                    <td style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;\">Téléchargez le fichier en cliquant sur le bouton ci-dessus</td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n\n                            <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td style=\"background-color: #ff8c00; color: white; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 12px;\">2</td>\n                                    <td style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;\">Décompressez l'archive ZIP sur votre ordinateur</td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n\n                            <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td style=\"background-color: #ff8c00; color: white; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 12px;\">3</td>\n                                    <td style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;\">Consultez le fichier README.txt pour les instructions détaillées</td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n\n                            <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td style=\"background-color: #ff8c00; color: white; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 12px;\">4</td>\n                                    <td style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;\">Intégrez les outils dans votre processus de conformité</td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n\n                <!-- SUPPORT -->\n                <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color: #e8f4f8; border: 1px solid #b3d9e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 25px 0; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>\n                            <strong style=\"color: #001f4d; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;\">❓ Des questions sur votre kit ?</strong>\n                            Consultez notre FAQ ou contactez-nous à <a href=\"mailto:contact@nexusconformite.fr\" style=\"color: #001f4d; text-decoration: none;\">contact@nexusconformite.fr</a>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n\n                <p class=\"text-block\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    Nous vous remercions d'avoir choisi NEXUS CONFORMITÉ. Nous sommes convaincus que ce kit vous sera très utile dans votre parcours de conformité.\n                </p>\n\n                <p class=\"text-block\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    À bientôt,<br>\n                    <strong style=\"color: #001f4d;\">L'équipe NEXUS CONFORMITÉ</strong>\n                </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- FOOTER -->\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"footer\" style=\"background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 25px 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">\n                <div class=\"footer-links\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\n                    <a href=\"[LIEN_DESABONNEMENT]\" style=\"color: #001f4d; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Me désabonner</a> |\n                    <a href=\"[LIEN_PREFERENCES]\" style=\"color: #001f4d; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Préférences</a> |\n                    <a href=\"[LIEN_FAQ]\" style=\"color: #001f4d; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">FAQ</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"company-info\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #777;\">\n                    <strong>NEXUS CONFORMITÉ</strong><br>\n                    Email: contact@nexusconformite.fr<br>\n                    Site: www.nexusconformite.fr<br>\n                    <br>\n                    © 2026 NEXUS CONFORMITÉ. Tous droits réservés.\n                </div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</body>\n</html>"
